messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图识别指向营销规划相关场景",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块错误地将用户的营销规划请求分类为“其他意图”（4001），导致后续流程完全偏离规划路径。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "output_summary.intent", "value": "4001"},
        {"source": "output_summary.intent_name", "value": "其他意图"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition.actual_stage", "value": "non_agent"},
        {"source": "reference_contract.expected_stage", "value": "intent"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "阶段路由进入有效响应流程",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "path_dispatch"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图被识别为4001，阶段直接路由至non_agent，未能进入澄清或规划阶段，且path_dispatch未纠正此错误阶段。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "output_summary.stage", "value": "non_agent"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition.evidence", "actual_stage": "non_agent"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "返回内容具备业务有效性",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition", "result_assembly", "planning_function"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因意图识别错误和非规划路由，planning_function生成0张卡片，result_assembly仅输出占位文本，无法提供任何业务内容。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "output_summary.card_summary", "value": "[]"},
        {"source": "output_summary.robot_text", "value": "卡片生成完成"},
        {"source": "execution_stage_probe.planning_function.evidence.card_count", "value": 0}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "参考合约要求阶段为intent，但意图识别输出阶段为non_agent，导致合约未满足。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "reference_contract.expected_stage", "value": "intent"},
        {"source": "output_summary.stage", "value": "non_agent"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["intent_recognition"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模块（intent_recognition）将包含明确营销规划关键词（“NBEV目标”、“增加理财师”、“优化产品方案”）的用户请求误分类为“其他意图”（4001），并直接输出阶段为non_agent。这是最早偏离参考合约的关键点，导致后续所有规划、澄清和内容生成步骤均未执行。",
  "evidence": [
    {"source": "execution_stage_probe.intent_recognition", "actual_stage": "non_agent", "expected_stage": "intent"},
    {"source": "output_summary.intent", "value": "4001"},
    {"source": "output_summary.intent_name", "value": "其他意图"},
    {"source": "reference_contract", "expected_stage": "intent", "scenario": "intent_recognition"},
    {"source": "output_summary.stage", "value": "non_agent"}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

